Safe-safe way:
```powershell
$p1 = $issue.PSObject.Properties['createdAt']
$p2 = $issue.PSObject.Properties['created_at']
$createdAt = if ($p1) { $p1.Value } elseif ($p2) { $p2.Value } else { $null }
```
This is robust.

